title: Stade Municipal (Kenitra)
text: Stade Municipal is a <a href="multi-purpose%20stadium">multi-purpose stadium</a> in <a href="Kenitra">Kenitra</a>, <a href="Morocco">Morocco</a> which has been inaugurated in 1941. It is currently used mostly for <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> matches and is the home stadium of <a href="KAC%20Kenitra">KAC Kenitra</a>. The stadium has a capacity of 15,000 people, and is currently in renovation. After the renovation the stadium will have a seating capacity between 30,000 and 40,000.
